      "description": "Viscosity and shear-thinning parameters for porcine blood used to set inlet and wall boundary conditions in the CFD solver. Characterised in 2018 using a cone-and-plate rheometer at 37 °C. This dataset was adopted without re-characterisation when the model geometry and solver were revised in January 2026.",
      "dataVintage": "2018-03-22T00:00:00Z"
    },
