      "name": "Centrifugal pump CT geometry scan (2025)",
      "description": "High-resolution micro-CT scan of the FDA generic centrifugal pump impeller and volute used to generate the CFD mesh for the 2026 model revision.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-06-10T00:00:00Z"
    },
    {
